# Voice & Tone

## Who's speaking
A guide who has been through the descent and came back with tools — calm, exacting, unafraid of the dark, ultimately on your side. Speaks to "you"; includes itself in "us." **Never a named founder.**

## Voice attributes
- **Initiatory** — invites you across a threshold ("Begin the descent").
- **Uncompromising, not harsh** — "was not built to comfort you," yet never cruel.
- **Rigorous** — grounds feeling in mechanism; cites the science.
- **Literary & spare** — short, weighted sentences; deliberate white space.
- **Quietly whimsical** — a light, wondrous lift so it never turns clinical-cold. Think **Dr. Joe Dispenza**: real neuroscience delivered as something a little awe-inspiring and human.
- **Collective & equal** — everyone is going through the same thing; the struggle is universal.

## Tone calibration — the Dispenza line
Science first, wonder second, spirituality never. Explain the mechanism (nervous system, neural pathways, microcurrent) and *then* let it feel transformational. **Accessible awe — not mysticism.**

## Tone by context
- **Hero / manifesto:** intense, initiatory, philosophical.
- **Product / how-it-works:** precise, confident, mechanism-led — still warm.
- **FAQ / support:** plain, honest, reassuring. The live site openly admits trade-offs — keep that honesty.
- **Email / social:** shorter, intimate, one idea per piece; the whimsical lift can come forward.
- **Claims / health:** careful, evidence-bound, asterisked where needed.

## Vocabulary — DO use
know · knowing · nervous system · neural pathways · conditioning · reconditioning · pattern · evidence · signal · ritual · practice · return · descent · excavation · integration · coherence · regulation · rigor · protocol · instrument · threshold · becoming.

## Vocabulary — DON'T use
- **No spiritual / "witchy" words:** manifest, magic, spell, energy healing, chakra, aura, moon rituals, crystals, vibration/vibes, divine, sacred, "the universe will provide," woo.
- **No hype / beauty clichés:** miracle, glow-up, game-changer, secret, anti-aging cure, "10x."
- **No cold jargon dumps** — never list clinical mechanism with no human meaning attached.
- **Avoid absolute medical claims** — keep efficacy careful and qualified.

## Before → after
1. **Cold:** "Microcurrent device that boosts collagen."
   **NŌS:** "An instrument, not a gadget. Microcurrent — clinical for decades — reframed as the daily signal that tells your nervous system something intentional is beginning."
2. **Woo:** "Manifest your highest self and raise your vibration."
   **NŌS:** "Make the unconscious conscious. The patterns running your life were written before you could choose them — this is how you meet them."
3. **Hype:** "Get glowing skin fast with our miracle wand!"
   **NŌS:** "Visible change your body can measure — not belief, evidence. Skin shifts you can see, in about 90 seconds a day."
